Items.c: <[>滅了藥王谷的兇手是摩尼教,怎麼會是毛毛？要是想留下兇手的名字,也該寫上摩尼教吧！<]>
Items.mt: <[>The murderer who destroyed Yakwang Valley was Manichaeism, how could it be Mao Mao? If you want to leave the name of the murderer, you should put Manichaeism on it too! <]>
